|               |   SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |     CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |       VirtualExecutionPlan name=sqlite compute_context=memory initial_sql=SELECT `hits`.`SearchPhrase`, count(1) AS `c` FROM `hits` WHERE (`hits`.`SearchPhrase` <> '') GROUP BY `hits`.`SearchPhrase` ORDER BY `c` DESC NULLS FIRST LIMIT 10 |
